<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1242317>
    dc:description "FIGURE 27. Anisepyris: strictus species-group. A. Pronotal disc in dorsal profile; B–C. Mesopleuron in frontal profile; venustus species-group. D–M. Head in dorsal profile.D. A. bregori sp. nov.; E. A. elrondi sp. nov.; F.A. fingolfini sp. nov.; G. A.fingoni sp. nov.; H.A.finrodi sp. nov.; I. A. finwei sp. nov.; J. A. feanori sp. nov.; K. A.galadrieli sp. nov.; L. A.galdorisp. nov.; M. A.gamilzirakisp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1242317/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1242319>
    dc:description "FIGURE 28. Anisepyris: venustus species-group. Head in dorsal profile. A. A. gelmiri sp. nov.; B. A. lalaithi sp. nov.; C. A. angulatus Santos & Azevedo, 2000; D. A. antiguensis Evans, 1966; E. A. attenuatus Santos, 2002; F. A. basilargus Santos & Azevedo, 2008; G. A. basipilosus Santos & Azevedo, 2000; H. A. dentatus Santos & Azevedo, 2000; I. A. eganellus (Westwood, 1874); J. A. grisselli Evans, 1979; K. A. lobatusSantos & Azevedo, 2000; L. A.rotundus Santos, 2002." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1242319/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1242321>
    dc:description "FIGURE 29. Anisepyris: venustus species-group. A–C. Head in dorsal profile. A. A. smithanus (Westwood, 1874); B. A. venustus Evans, 1964 (♂); C. A. venustus Evans, 1964 (♀);D–E. Mandible in frontal profile; G–J.Mesosoma in dorsal profile; K–M. Mesopleuron in frontal profile." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1242321/files/figure.png" ;
